condition.narrative: Schedule 2, Section I.A.1(b) of the Loan Agreement: Co-financing from CBJ in an amount equivalent to US$13,880,000 no later than 45days from Effective Date.
Schedule 2, Section I.A.2(d) of the Loan Agreement: Recruitment of an ISSF Manager no later than 90 days from Effective Date.
Schedule 2, Section I.A.2(e) of the Loan Agreement: Recruitment of a Senior Accountant no later than 90 days from Effective Date.
Schedule 2, Section I.A.2(f) of the Loan Agreement: Adoption of the Enterprise Resource Planning, or other accounting softwaresystem no later than 180 days from Effective Date.
Schedule 2, Section I.A.2(h) of the Loan Agreement: Hire an external auditor of ISSF no later than 6 months after Effective Date.
Schedule 2, Section I.A.2(j) of the Loan Agreement: Establishment of an Investment Committee within 180 days of Effective Date.
